    "created_at": "2016-03-22T09:16:50Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-03-22T09:19:46Z",
    "body": "While that may work, hardcoding the positions will incur maintenance if you ever change resolutions/monitor positions. It's best if you use the [screen module](http://electron.atom.io/docs/v0.37.2/api/screen/) and use the [`win.setBounds(...)` method](http://electron.atom.io/docs/v0.37.2/api/browser-window/#winsetboundsoptions-animate).\n\n**EDIT:** Also, the Electron guys prefer you keep questions like this in the [community](https://github.com/atom/electron#community) and actual issues in this tracker.\n"
  },
